title: Fox Wake Presents | Vegas or Busted
description:
Vegas and wake boarding are two words you would probably never use together in a sentence.
Where most see an opportunity to party, Fox's wake team saw an opening to put in some work.
Doing things a little differently in "Sin City, " Grant Roberts and Jimmy LaRiche hopped fences, set up winches, crashed pool parties and ran from security.
